tracks time spent with x,y,z apps open and at the front of screen

or

time spent focused on app you choose to focus on

with keyboard shortcuts

i.e. shift-space brings up "What do you want to focus on?"
and you select one of your windows
it can then either count all time spent with that window at forefront until shift-space again
or lock it on screen for x amount of time
or set up intervals for you to take breaks at

Log, Lock, Level.
Log total amount of time spent focusing on (my target(s) of focus)
Lock me to focusing on this thing until I specifically decide to end it.
Level out my time spent on x for me. 